CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, October 24, 1959, pg. 3 reads: "Rescued - Police rescued John (Rocky) Nelson, 72, from the Braddock fire which killed three children"
TitMainTitle: Portrait of John "Rocky" Nelson seated at table with coffee cup, in interior with wallpaper with ivy planted in clocks, teacups, and watering cans
